SUMMARY:Mrs. Doubtfire
DESCRIPTION:A new musical comedy about the things we do to stay together\n			\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				Based on the beloved film\, Mrs. Doubtfire tells the hysterical and heartfelt story of an out-of-work actor who will do anything for his kids. ItтАЩs тАЬthe lovable\, big-hearted musical comedy we need right now\,тАЭ raves the Chicago Tribune тАУ one that proves weтАЩre better together. \n			\n			\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n			\n			\n				\n				\n				\n				\n			\n				\n				\n			\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				CRITICAL ACCLAIM FOR MRS. DOUBTFIRE\n			\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n					\n			\n			\n			\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n					\n			\n			\n			\n					тАУ The Telegraph \n					\n					тАЬSharp\, funny\, and full of heart.тАЭ \n					\n				\n				\n			\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n					\n			\n			\n			\n					тАУ The Hollywood Reporter \n					\n					тАЬA feel-good\, family-friendly musical comedy that delivers.тАЭ \n					\n				\n				\n			\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n					\n			\n			\n			\n					тАУ Chicago Tribune/Daily News \n					\n					тАЬThis lovable\, big-hearted musical comedy delivers a good time for all ages.тАЭ \n					\n				\n				\n			\n			\n				\n			\n			\n				\n				\n				\n				\n			\n				\n				\n			\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				PERFORMANCE SCHEDULE\n			\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n					\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				яБФTuesday\, Oct 13\, 7:30 p.m. тАФ H-E-B Community Night\n			\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				яБФWednesday\, Oct 14\, 7:30 p.m. \n			\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				яБФThursday\, Oct 15\, 7:30 p.m. тАФ Out@TUTS Afterparty\n			\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				яБФFriday\, Oct 16\, 8 p.m. \n			\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				яБФSaturday\, Oct 17\, 2 p.m. \n			\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				яБФSaturday\, O