SUMMARY:DisneyтАЩs The Little Mermaid
DESCRIPTION:This holiday season\, be part of our world!\n			\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				DisneyтАЩs The Little Mermaid is a dazzling musical adventure based on the beloved Hans Christian Andersen tale and classic animated film. Featuring unforgettable music by eight-time Academy Award┬о winner Alan Menken\, with lyrics by Howard Ashman and Glenn Slater\, this Broadway-sized spectacular follows Ariel\, a curious young mermaid who dreams of life above the Sea. Relive all the moments you love with songs like тАЬUnder the Sea\,тАЭ тАЬKiss the Girl\,тАЭ and тАЬPart of Your World.тАЭ This enchanting production created by Theatre Under The Stars is this holidayтАЩs hottest ticket. \n			\n			\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n			\n			\n				\n				\n				\n				\n			\n				\n				\n			\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				CRITICAL ACCLAIM FOR THE LITTLE MERMAID\n			\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n					\n			\n			\n			\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n					\n			\n			\n			\n					- Houston Chronicle \n					\n					тАЬThis intricate and enjoyable production will leave you swimming in a sea of fun and wonder.тАЭ \n					\n				\n				\n			\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n					\n			\n			\n			\n					- Broadway World тАУ Houston\n					\n					тАЬThis production does your favorite childhood movie justice and then some.тАЭ\n					\n				\n				\n			\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n					\n			\n			\n			\n					- Houston Press \n					\n					тАЬWhat a splendid production тАж Theatre Under the StarsтАЩ spirited rendition rivals any Broadway house.тАЭ \n					\n				\n				\n			\n			\n				\n			\n			\n				\n				\n				\n				\n			\n				\n				\n			\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				PERFORMANCE SCHEDULE\n			\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n					\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				яБФTuesday\, Dec 