lable for $35 at the box office for mezzanine and gallery seating starting 2 hours prior to curtain. \nQuestions about parking\, dining or other aspects of attending a TUTS show? WeтАЩve got answers! \n			\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				RUN TIME\n2 hours and 30 minutes including intermission\n			\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				CONTENT NOTICE\nDisneyтАЩs The Little Mermaid is intended for guests 6 and up. All guests require a ticket\, regardless of age. \n			\n			\n				\n				\n				\n				\n			\n				\n				\n			\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				Photos\n			\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n					\n                \n                    \n                        \n                            \n                            \n                        \n                    \n                \n                    \n                        \n                            \n                            \n                        \n                    \n                \n                    \n                        \n                            \n                            \n                        \n                    \n                \n                    \n                        \n                            \n                            \n                        \n                    \n                \n                    \n                        \n                            \n                            \n                        \n                    \n                \n                    \n                        \n                            \n                            \n                        \n                    \n                \n                    \n                        \n                            \n                            \n                        \n                    \n                \n                    \n                        \n                            \n       