SUMMARY:The WhoтАЩs Tommy
DESCRIPTION:The groundbreaking rock musical that changed Broadway forever\n			\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				In 1969\, The Who created a rock opera that changed the course of music history. Myth and spectacle combine in this fresh reinvention that includes the unforgettable anthems тАЬIтАЩm Free\,тАЭ тАЬSee Me\, Feel Me\,тАЭ тАЬSensationтАЭ and тАЬPinball Wizard.тАЭ After witnessing a murder\, the young Tommy Walker is lost in the universe\, endlessly and obsessively staring into the mirror. An innate knack for pinball catapults him from reticent adolescent to celebrity savior. Tony Award-winning composer Pete Townshend and Tony Award┬о-winning original director Des McAnuff find powerful resonance reexamining this classic story for today.\n			\n			\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n			\n			\n				\n				\n				\n				\n			\n				\n				\n			\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				CRITICAL ACCLAIM FOR TOMMY\n			\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n					\n			\n			\n			\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n					\n			\n			\n			\n					тАУ Entertainment Weekly \n					\n					тАЬSee it. Feel it. You wonтАЩt forget it.тАЭ \n					\n				\n				\n			\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n					\n			\n			\n			\n					тАУ The Wall Street Journal \n					\n					тАЬThunderous and thoroughly intoxicating.тАЭ \n					\n				\n				\n			\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n					\n			\n			\n			\n					тАУ Deadline\n					\n					тАЬA sensation! A non-stop surge of electrified energy.тАЭ \n					\n				\n				\n			\n			\n				\n			\n			\n				\n				\n				\n				\n			\n				\n				\n			\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				PERFORMANCE SCHEDULE\n			\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n					\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				яБФTuesday\, Feb 2\, 7:30 p.m. тАФ H-E-B Community Night\n			\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				яБФWednesda