or other aspects of attending a TUTS show? WeтАЩve got answers! \n			\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				RUN TIME\n1 hour and 20 minutes\n			\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				CONTENT NOTICE\nOh\, Mary! contains explicit language\, adult themes and comedic material intended for mature audiences. This production features water-based haze and one single gunshot. \n			\n			\n				\n				\n				\n				\n			\n				\n				\n			\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				Photos\n			\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n					\n                \n                    \n                        \n                            \n                            \n                        \n                    \n                \n                    \n                        \n                            \n                            \n                        \n                    \n                \n                    \n                        \n                            \n                            \n                        \n                    \n                \n                    \n                        \n                            \n                            \n                        \n                    \n                \n                    \n                        \n                            \n                            \n                        \n                    \n                \n                    \n                        \n                            \n                            \n                        \n                    \n                \n                    \n                        \n                            \n                            \n                        \n                    \n                \n             \n				\n			\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				Emilio Madrid\n			\n			\n				\n				\n				\n				\n			\n				\n				\n			\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n	