DESCRIPTION:юАг\n					\n						FRIDAY\, MAY 14\, 2027 ┬╖ 7:00 PM\n						\n					\n				\n			\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n					юВБ\n					\n						The hobby center\n						\n					\n				\n			\n			\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n					юБа\n					\n						Info\n						Produced by Theatre Under The Stars\nFeaturing HoustonтАЩs top high school musical theatre students.\n					\n				\n			\n			\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				ON SALE SPRING 2027\nSTAY TUNED FOR DETAILS \n			\n			\n				\n				\n				\n				\n			\n				\n				\n			\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				Where HoustonтАЩs Future Broadway Legends Shine\n			\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				The Tommy Tune Awards are the cityтАЩs biggest night for high school musical theatre тАФ a high-energy celebration spotlighting the most talented student performers\, designers\, and directors in the region. \nCreated and produced by Theatre Under The Stars\, this electrifying ceremony honors excellence on and off the stage\, with showstopping performances and unforgettable moments inspired by the legacy of Broadway legend and Houston native Tommy Tune. \n┬а \n			\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				┬а ┬а SPONSORED BY \n			\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n			\n				Sign Up for Ticket Alerts\n			\n			\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n			\n			\n				\n				\n				\n				\n			\n				\n				\n			\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n					\n				\n			\n				FIND OUT MORE ABOUT THE TOMMY TUNE AWARDS
